Package: RCTC
Type: Package
Title: The Rotated Combination of Two-Component Ground Motions
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Pengfei", "Wang", email = "wltcwpf@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/wltcwpf/RCTC
BugReports: https://github.com/wltcwpf/RCTC/issues
Description: This package initially aimed at calculating the Rotated Combination of Two-Component Ground Motions (e.g., RotD50 for PSA at different oscillator periods). Now the package has been expanded to include other commonly used intensity measure metrics (e.g., IA, CAV, and EAS, etc.) 
